-- Mercer says terminated Pimco, Western Asset as subadvisors on a bond fund -SEC
-- By Jennifer Ablan
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 03:55PM EDT
-- None



April 4 (Reuters) - Mercer Investment Management, Inc. has terminated Pacific Investment Management Company LLC and Western Asset Management Company as subadvisors to the Mercer Core Fixed Income Fund, effective immediately, according to an SEC filing on Thursday.

